RogueStar Animation and Graphics Library

-----	Documentation

The documentation for RSAGL can be built by typing:

$ make doc

This requires a working latex installation.  (/usr/bin/pdflatex)

-----	The Partial Monad

You need to have the Partial monad installed in a directory parallel to rsagl.

$ darcs get --partial http://www.downstairspeople.org/darcs/partial

-----	Running Tests

$ make tests
$ ./rsagl-tests
